.docname {Domains Overview}
.include {docs}

The **Domains** view provides a straightforward, organized overview of all the environments your account is linked to.

---

## Navigating the Domains View

At the top of the Domains screen, you'll find a control bar designed to help you quickly find or add new environments:

* **Search Bar:** A quick text filter to find a specific domain in your list instantly.
* **Enter Private Domain:** Click this button to request access or log into a private organizational domain.
* **Create New Domain:** Opens the domain creation wizard (this button is restricted to users with administrative privileges).

## The Domains Table

Below the controls is the main **Domains Table**. This table lists all the Main Domains and Subdomains you are a member of, displaying the domain names and the specific roles (e.g., Admin, Member) you hold in each one.